UNDERLYING SOURCE DATA

The variety records aggregated in `data/varieties.parquet` remain under the
licenses of their original publishers:

  - AGRA / CESSA varietycatalogues.com — open access, attribution requested
  - PPV&FRA India (plantauthority.gov.in/node/3044) — Government of India open data
  - NACGRAB Nigeria (nacgrab.gov.ng) — Federal Ministry of Science & Technology
  - ECOWAS-UEMOA-CILSS Regional Catalogue — regional public document
  - Ghana 2019 National Crop Variety Catalogue (CSIR-CRI / NASTAG) — public
  - KEPHIS Kenya National Crop Variety List (kephis.go.ke) — public
  - FAO WIEWS Indicator 40 (fao.org/wiews) — FAO open data
  - CIMMYT Maize Catalog (maizecatalog.cimmyt.org) — public catalog

When redistributing this dataset, attribute both this aggregation work AND
the relevant underlying sources for the rows you use.
